{"type": "article", "id": 15983, "title": "Lift Up Storage System", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-13T06:10:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135735Ilv4wWxpcrHCThb0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款升降挂衣杆来自俄罗斯的著名设计师 Igor Lobanov，它的外面覆盖了一面镜子，和里面的挂杆一起通过滑轮升降，就能将挂着的衣服或伞等杂物隐藏在镜子里，以保持墙面的整洁。这个设计同样适用于置物柜，柜子滑下来时，小朋友也就能取拿东西了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143414ahd5ULCyDgEq2RFW.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"732\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143415L0UsAkxo9cNgWjKw.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"414\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.39428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143415NPjE6VI9tTSloyk2.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"797\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}